1
00:00:04,045 --> 00:00:04,739
Get out!
出去！

2
00:00:07,081 --> 00:00:09,049
Get out! Hurry!
出去…快出去！

3
00:00:18,059 --> 00:00:19,117
Inside the hut! Come on!
躲進去…快點…

4
00:00:19,227 --> 00:00:20,091
Get in! Come on!
進去…快一點…

5
00:00:22,396 --> 00:00:23,328
Out of here!
出去！

6
00:00:23,431 --> 00:00:25,956
Don't come in! Get out!
不要再進來了…出去…

7
00:00:27,668 --> 00:00:29,295
Come on! Run!
快點！快跑…

8
00:00:41,449 --> 00:00:42,279
Yes, sir
是…

9
00:00:44,118 --> 00:00:46,211
Is it Mehebu Clan?
馬赫坡社嗎？

10
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:47,309
Yes, sir
是…

11
00:00:50,258 --> 00:00:53,921
Aim all cannons at the Mehebu Forest
砲口全部對準馬赫坡森林…

12
00:00:55,763 --> 00:00:59,631
End this battle before the sun's out
太陽出來之前結束這場戰爭吧！

13
00:01:04,972 --> 00:01:06,735
Tado! Kill me!
達多…

14
00:01:06,841 --> 00:01:08,968
快把我殺了！

15
00:01:09,076 --> 00:01:10,441
Come on!
快！

16
00:01:11,646 --> 00:01:13,841
It hurts so badly!
我好痛…

17
00:01:16,984 --> 00:01:18,508
Out of the way!
讓開！讓開…

18
00:01:20,121 --> 00:01:22,783
Cut my head off! You hear me?
把我的頭砍下來聽不懂啊…

19
00:01:27,328 --> 00:01:28,522
Get off him!
手拿開…

20
00:02:28,856 --> 00:02:31,222
It's beautiful
好漂亮…

21
00:02:31,859 --> 00:02:33,884
So beautiful
好漂亮啊…

22
00:02:36,897 --> 00:02:38,865
So beautiful
好漂亮啊…

23
00:02:56,550 --> 00:02:57,949
Stop firing please
請停止射擊…

24
00:02:58,052 --> 00:02:59,610
They ran away
他們逃掉了…

25
00:03:32,353 --> 00:03:39,725
Fight till you drop! Seediq Bale!
戰死吧！賽德克巴萊…

26
00:04:07,521 --> 00:04:09,182
Fire the cannons! Fire!
開砲！開砲！

27
00:04:11,492 --> 00:04:12,754
We're under attack!
敵人打來了…

28
00:04:20,134 --> 00:04:23,194
You damned Japanese! Get out of our territory!
可惡的日本人…滾開我們的部落…

29
00:04:32,046 --> 00:04:33,809
You bastards! Get out!
混蛋…還不快滾…

30
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:51,928
That's one favor I did you Mehebus today
helping you drive our the intruders
今天幫你把異族人趕出馬赫坡一次…

31
00:05:03,210 --> 00:05:05,337
Out of my way! Let me kill them!
前面讓開…我來打！

32
00:05:34,441 --> 00:05:35,601
Temu, give me the bullets!
泰牧…把子彈給我！

33
00:05:36,777 --> 00:05:38,210
Come on! Look out!
快點…小心前面！

34
00:05:45,953 --> 00:05:46,749
Climb up there!
爬上去！

35
00:05:55,896 --> 00:05:57,523
Sine! Sine!
西奈…西奈…

36
00:05:57,631 --> 00:05:59,155
Sine!
西奈…

37
00:05:59,266 --> 00:06:03,225
Sine! Sine!
西奈…西奈…

38
00:06:03,971 --> 00:06:04,801
Stop!
站住！

39
00:06:05,773 --> 00:06:07,297
Come back here!
給我站住！

40
00:06:07,408 --> 00:06:08,272
You take care of him!
去照顧他…

41
00:06:37,838 --> 00:06:40,170
Load the guns! Come on!
裝子彈！快！

42
00:06:42,810 --> 00:06:43,834
Pawan?
巴萬…

43
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:02,287
You Japanese are finished!
日本人你們完蛋了…

44
00:07:42,169 --> 00:07:44,228
Quick! - Catch him!
-快點…
-追過去！

45
00:07:44,571 --> 00:07:46,471
Off with his head!
獵下他的頭！

46
00:07:46,874 --> 00:07:48,000
Stop!
不要跑…

47
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:54,711
Don't let him slip away!
不要放過他…

48
00:08:02,423 --> 00:08:04,186
Mouna Rudo!
莫那魯道…

49
00:08:04,925 --> 00:08:05,892
Stop running!
大家不要逃了！

50
00:08:07,428 --> 00:08:09,225
Kill until our blood runs out!
殺到血乾吧…

51
00:08:09,730 --> 00:08:12,096
Cut off their heads like true warriors!
像戰士一樣拿下人頭…

52
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:15,634
The heavenly home of our ancestors,
here we come!
回祖靈之家唷…

53
00:10:25,866 --> 00:10:27,857
I'm a chief, not your little brother
我是頭目…不是你弟弟…

54
00:10:36,543 --> 00:10:38,670
Iyung! Iyung!
伊勇…伊勇…

55
00:10:50,524 --> 00:10:52,890
Don't touch it, lyung
手不要碰…伊勇…

56
00:10:53,927 --> 00:10:54,689
Iyung!
伊勇…

57
00:10:58,732 --> 00:11:01,030
What are you doing? Move!
幹什麼…走開！

58
00:11:02,769 --> 00:11:04,532
Look out! It's falling down!
倒下去了…倒下去了…

59
00:11:05,706 --> 00:11:07,105
Pawan! Get out of there!
巴萬！快出來！

60
00:11:08,942 --> 00:11:11,536
Pawan, get out now!
巴萬…快點出來！

61
00:11:14,047 --> 00:11:14,979
Pawan!
巴萬…

62
00:11:15,516 --> 00:11:17,074
Iyung! Iyung!
伊勇…伊勇…

63
00:11:17,184 --> 00:11:18,151
Are you alright?
你怎麼了？

64
00:11:18,252 --> 00:11:19,981
Pawan, I've got a good gun
巴萬！拿到好槍了…

65
00:11:20,888 --> 00:11:21,616
What's wrong?
怎麼了？

66
00:11:23,056 --> 00:11:24,421
Batu! -Dakis!
-巴杜…
-達基司

67
00:11:26,426 --> 00:11:27,188
Move!
走開！

68
00:11:27,895 --> 00:11:28,623
Ubus!
烏布斯…

69
00:11:51,785 --> 00:11:53,753
Come on! The Japanese are out!
快…日本人跑出來了…

70
00:12:05,132 --> 00:12:06,292
Watch out over there!
小心那邊！

71
00:12:14,007 --> 00:12:15,474
There's one behind him!
後面還有一個…

72
00:12:22,583 --> 00:12:23,515
Don't go there!
不要過去！

73
00:12:36,129 --> 00:12:37,289
Stop!
不要跑！

74
00:15:33,473 --> 00:15:34,940
Bomb!
砲彈！

75
00:17:36,630 --> 00:17:39,155
So you're Mouna Rudo
原來你就是莫那魯道…

76
00:17:42,469 --> 00:17:45,905
Now I see you clearly
我看清楚你了…

77
00:17:48,942 --> 00:17:50,375
Tado, how do we dodge those cannons?
達多…

78
00:17:50,477 --> 00:17:52,342
怎樣才能躲過那些大砲？

79
00:17:58,318 --> 00:17:59,842
Chief, let this ghost lead the way
頭目…

80
00:17:59,953 --> 00:18:02,581
讓我這個鬼魂來帶路吧！

81
00:18:13,099 --> 00:18:14,726
Fire!
開砲！

82
00:19:09,522 --> 00:19:10,819
Look!
看！

83
00:19:10,924 --> 00:19:14,155
Cherry blossoms everywhere!
櫻花開滿天了…

84
00:20:06,345 --> 00:20:09,715
(Those who come forward voluntarily
will be spared)

85
00:20:09,715 --> 00:20:12,735
(Come to the shelters to surrender)

86
00:20:20,860 --> 00:20:25,422
l'm crossing the rainbow bridge
我要走去彼岸的那邊了…

87
00:20:25,532 --> 00:20:30,367
l am Mouna Rudo
我是莫那魯道唷！

88
00:20:30,470 --> 00:20:35,339
Look at the road l've trodden
看我腳步所邁開的道路！

89
00:20:40,113 --> 00:20:42,547
No one's ever gonna stop us
誰也無法抵擋我們…

90
00:20:42,649 --> 00:20:44,947
The determined warriors
決死的勇士啊！

91
00:20:45,051 --> 00:20:49,954
We're home with our enemy's heads
看我們今天帶著首級歸來了…

92
00:20:50,056 --> 00:20:55,153
We're true warriors, like budding pine leaves
像松樹嫩芽般真正的勇士啊！

93
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:10,404
You must be starved
大家都餓了吧…

94
00:21:10,510 --> 00:21:12,535
and you must be exhausted
也都累了吧！

95
00:21:13,713 --> 00:21:16,204
It's time to decide your future
是該決定自己未來的時侯了…

96
00:21:18,384 --> 00:21:21,717
If you want to take your own life, do it
想自盡的就自盡

97
00:21:21,821 --> 00:21:24,051
If you want to turn yourself in, go ahead
想投降的就投降

98
00:21:26,059 --> 00:21:28,152
If you want to keep fighting..
想繼續戰鬥的…

99
00:21:29,596 --> 00:21:30,392
Tado..
達多…

100
00:21:32,332 --> 00:21:33,822
My dear son..
我的兒子啊…

101
00:21:36,202 --> 00:21:38,170
The hero of Mehebu Clan
馬赫坡的勇者！

102
00:21:39,139 --> 00:21:42,267
Lead them to fight
until you use up all your bullets
你帶他們打完最後一顆子彈吧！

103
00:21:42,375 --> 00:21:43,205
Father! -Chief..
父親！

104
00:21:43,309 --> 00:21:44,708
頭目…

105
00:21:44,811 --> 00:21:46,073
Warriors, forgive me
戰士們！

106
00:21:47,147 --> 00:21:48,546
原諒我…

107
00:21:50,517 --> 00:21:51,575
Forgive me
原諒我…

108
00:21:53,753 --> 00:21:57,587
I don't want the Japanese to insult me
in front of my people
我不願讓日本人在族人面前玩弄我

109
00:21:58,424 --> 00:21:59,686
Forgive me
原諒我…

110
00:22:02,529 --> 00:22:05,589
I'll be waiting for you on the mountain peak
我到山的極巔等你們…

111
00:22:07,333 --> 00:22:10,393
Let's cross the rainbow bridge together
to the eternal hunting ground
一起回到彩虹彼端的美麗獵場…

112
00:22:14,941 --> 00:22:16,101
Father?
父親…

113
00:22:19,979 --> 00:22:21,606
Go..Seediq Bale!
去吧！

114
00:22:21,714 --> 00:22:23,238
賽德克巴萊！

115
00:22:59,686 --> 00:23:00,675
Chief Mouna?
莫那頭目…

116
00:23:02,121 --> 00:23:03,349
Bakan,
巴岡…

117
00:23:03,456 --> 00:23:07,017
bring over everyone from the chief's family
把我們家族的人都帶過來…

118
00:23:07,126 --> 00:23:08,252
Iwan, go back and tell our people in the cavern
依婉…

119
00:23:08,895 --> 00:23:11,056
回去告訴岩窟的族人

120
00:23:11,164 --> 00:23:13,564
that those who don't want to surrender
may as well kill themselves
不想投降的就自盡吧！

121
00:23:13,666 --> 00:23:15,190
I want to fight!
我要去戰鬥…

122
00:23:15,268 --> 00:23:15,859
Me too! -It's over!
我也要去…

123
00:23:15,969 --> 00:23:17,129
結束了…

124
00:23:17,837 --> 00:23:19,031
Mouna!
莫那！

125
00:23:19,138 --> 00:23:22,539
Mouna, where's your ancestral spirit?
莫那…你的祖靈在哪裡？

126
00:23:26,980 --> 00:23:29,642
Where is it?
你的祖靈在哪裡…

127
00:23:33,786 --> 00:23:39,247
There could be greater suffering if you survived
我怕你們承擔不住活下來…

128
00:23:56,476 --> 00:23:59,274
Wipe your face clean
…把臉擦乾淨

129
00:24:30,610 --> 00:24:34,410
Thank you, women and children
謝謝你們女人孩子…

130
00:24:34,514 --> 00:24:38,883
for sacrificing yourselves
to complete the men's souls
成就了部落男人的靈魂…

131
00:26:53,453 --> 00:26:56,945
She's awake!
醒來了…

132
00:26:57,056 --> 00:26:58,956
That savage woman is awake!
那個蕃女醒來了…

133
00:26:59,058 --> 00:27:01,891
Officer Kabasoa!
樺澤警部…樺澤警部…

134
00:27:03,463 --> 00:27:04,555
What's going on?
-That savage woman is awake
-怎麼了？
-那個蕃女醒來了…

135
00:27:04,664 --> 00:27:06,188
Is it Mahung? -Yes, sir
-是馬紅嗎？
-是…

136
00:27:07,400 --> 00:27:08,367
Excuse me!
不好意思…

137
00:27:09,569 --> 00:27:10,797
Excuse me!
不好意思…

138
00:27:10,903 --> 00:27:12,234
Let me through!
…借過

139
00:27:13,706 --> 00:27:16,072
Mahung! Mahung!
馬紅…馬紅…

140
00:27:18,211 --> 00:27:19,303
Mahung..
馬紅…

141
00:27:19,412 --> 00:27:21,539
I'm Kabasawa. I've been to your house
我是樺澤…

142
00:27:21,647 --> 00:27:24,377
我去過你們家的…

143
00:27:24,484 --> 00:27:27,044
Do you remember me, Mahung?
記得嗎？馬紅…

144
00:27:31,357 --> 00:27:33,848
Why did you save me?
…為什麼要救我？

145
00:27:35,795 --> 00:27:42,223
My husband and children are waiting for me
我的丈夫孩子都在等我啊…

146
00:27:44,871 --> 00:27:46,065
Mahong..
馬紅…

147
00:27:54,747 --> 00:27:55,736
100 dollars
一百塊錢！

148
00:27:56,716 --> 00:27:58,843
Son of a bitch! What are you doing?
混蛋！你們幹什麼？

149
00:27:58,951 --> 00:28:00,111
Don't put it on the desk!
不要放在桌子上！

150
00:28:01,454 --> 00:28:02,887
What are you looking at? Next!
看什麼？下一個…

151
00:28:02,989 --> 00:28:05,116
It's only a child. You can't get 100 for it
這只是孩子，哪值一百塊？

152
00:28:05,224 --> 00:28:06,122
Get it off!
拿走開！

153
00:28:06,225 --> 00:28:08,625
It's Temu Mouna from Truwan Clan
這是塔羅灣的…泰牧摩那…

154
00:28:08,728 --> 00:28:10,662
What child?
Don't you see the tattoos on his face?
什麼孩子，他臉上有圖騰哪！

155
00:28:10,763 --> 00:28:12,697
Put it over there! What a nuisance!
拿到那邊去啦，囉嗦…

156
00:28:12,798 --> 00:28:16,290
It's Tanah Robe, the Boarung chief
這是…波阿崙頭目達那哈羅拜…

157
00:28:21,574 --> 00:28:24,634
One of you from Gungu Clan killed our chief
你們荷戈社殺了我們頭目…

158
00:28:47,133 --> 00:28:52,730
This one is Pawan Nawi from Mehebu Clan
這是馬赫坡的巴萬那威…

159
00:28:55,274 --> 00:28:57,367
Ukan! Tado!
烏干…達多…

160
00:28:57,476 --> 00:29:00,172
Where are you?
你們在哪裡？

161
00:29:01,547 --> 00:29:06,644
Where is that father going?
那個父親要去哪裡哪？

162
00:29:06,752 --> 00:29:12,486
The father carrying a child on his back
那個父親揹著幼小的嬰孩…

163
00:29:12,592 --> 00:29:19,657
is setting out to shoot the two suns in the sky
要去征伐天上的兩顆太陽了！

164
00:29:19,765 --> 00:29:25,101
They go on and on for a long way
他們走了很遠很遠的路

165
00:29:25,204 --> 00:29:37,844
The child grows up
那個嬰孩長大成人了…

166
00:29:37,950 --> 00:29:43,513
The father dies at an old age
那個父親老死了…

167
00:29:43,623 --> 00:29:56,434
The child takes his father's bow and arrows
孩子揹起了父親的弓箭

168
00:29:56,535 --> 00:30:02,337
The child follows his father's footsteps
孩子繼續父親的路…

169
00:30:02,441 --> 00:30:14,911
toward the rising suns
向著日出之處前進

170
00:30:15,021 --> 00:30:20,857
He gets there at last
…終於到達了呀！

171
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:33,464
The child gets there at last
孩子終於到達了！

172
00:30:33,572 --> 00:30:39,101
The child shoots a sun down with an arrow
孩子張弓射下了一個太陽

173
00:30:39,211 --> 00:30:51,248
The sun loses its rays
太陽的光芒消失了

174
00:30:51,357 --> 00:30:56,693
The dead sun becomes the moon
死去的太陽變成了月亮

175
00:30:56,796 --> 00:31:09,573
He's a sun-shooting hero
他是射日的英雄！

176
00:31:09,675 --> 00:31:15,204
The sun-shooting hero is returning home
射日勇士又啟程歸鄉了！

177
00:31:15,314 --> 00:31:28,717
The sun-shooting hero has come a long,
long way
射日勇士走了很遠很遠的路…

178
00:31:28,828 --> 00:31:34,528
The sun-shooting hero is home at last
射日勇士終於回家了！

179
00:31:34,633 --> 00:31:47,671
But the hero is already gray-headed
勇士回家已經白髮蒼蒼…

180
00:31:53,519 --> 00:31:56,784
l am drunk today
今天的日子我醉了

181
00:31:56,889 --> 00:31:58,948
l saw him on the way
在路上我看到他了…

182
00:31:59,058 --> 00:32:00,753
The boy from the freezing winter
那個來自酷寒嚴冬下的男孩

183
00:32:00,860 --> 00:32:04,455
A fair-skinned boy like a budding pine leaf
如松枝嫩芽般白白的男孩

184
00:32:04,563 --> 00:32:06,463
Let's dance together
一起來跳舞吧…

185
00:32:06,565 --> 00:32:08,157
Let's enjoy ourselves
讓我們盡興歡聚吧！

186
00:32:08,267 --> 00:32:11,703
l'm drunk today
今天的日子我醉了

187
00:32:11,804 --> 00:32:15,399
Young girls, let's dance together
年輕的女孩我們一起跳舞吧…

188
00:32:17,243 --> 00:32:18,540
Surrender? Why should we surrender?
投降？

189
00:32:19,578 --> 00:32:21,341
為什麼要投降呢？

190
00:32:22,848 --> 00:32:24,645
We've had our enemy's sake wine
我們幾個既然喝了敵人的酒

191
00:32:25,851 --> 00:32:28,081
Doesn't that mean conciliation?
不就算和解了嗎？

192
00:32:28,187 --> 00:32:30,246
Why do we have to surrender?
為什麼還需要投降呢？…

193
00:32:33,993 --> 00:32:35,460
Tado... -Say no more!
-達多…
-不要再講了！

194
00:32:41,767 --> 00:32:43,530
Come on, drink with me
來！你也喝…

195
00:32:59,919 --> 00:33:00,817
Mahung, my little sister...
馬紅…

